content.text:
I'm ready to help you explore the codebase and design implementation plans for PsicoAlianza. I understand this is a Laravel 11-based SaaS platform for psychometric testing and HR management, following a strict Controller-Service-Repository architecture.

I can help you with:
- Exploring the codebase structure and existing patterns
- Designing implementation approaches for new features
- Identifying critical files and dependencies
- Creating detailed step-by-step implementation strategies
- Following the established architectural patterns and conventions

Please provide me with your requirements and any specific perspective you'd like me to apply during the design process. I'll thoroughly explore the relevant parts of the codebase and create a comprehensive implementation plan.

Note: I'm operating in read-only mode, so I'll only explore and plan - no file modifications will be made.
